Ing '''Lonely Planet''' ing pekamaragul a maglimbag kareng giya ampong ''digital media'' king pamagbiahi king mabilug a yatu. Aniang mumuna, maki lagiu yang Lonely Planet Publications, oneng miyalilan ya king Lonely Planet aniang Julio 2009 bang ipalto ing maleparan nang yampang king industria ning pamagbiahi/pamaglakbe, ampo ing ulagang bibie na kareng productung ''digital''. Kaibat da reng [[Let's Go Travel Guides]], metung ya kareng mumunang serie da reng libru king pamagbiahi para kareng [[:en:backpacking (travel)|backpacker]] ampong aliwang magbiahing mura. Aniang 2009, magpalual yang 500 a pamagat kareng 8 amanu, at makapisali yang maigit anam a miliun a ''guidebook'',{{Fact|date=January 2009}} bukud pa kareng programa king TV, magasin, aplicacion kareng cellphone ampong karinan king Aptas o website.    

Atin yang television production company ing Lonely Planet, ing ,<ref>[http://www.lonelyplanettelevision.com/ Lonely Planet Television]</ref> a mekalalang nang apat a serie: ''[[Lonely Planet Six Degrees]]'', ''The Sport Traveller'', ''Going Bush'', ''Vintage New Zealand'' ampong ''Bluelist Australia''. Makasentru ya ing Lonely Planet king [[Footscray]], metung a karulun (''suburb'') ning [[Melbourne]], [[Australia]], at atin yang makaugneng oficina king London ampong Oakland, California.

Manibat aniang 2007, ing tatalan king cumpania ya pin ing [[BBC Worldwide]], a maki 75% a bandi, kabang deng mitátag king cumpania, di Maureen ampong Tony Wheeler, ing tatalan king mitatagan a 25%.

Aniang 2009, migumpisa yang maglimbag bulanang magasin a maki lagiung Lonely Planet Magazine ing Lonely Planet.

Ibat ya ing lagiu ning cumpania king metung a gulis a e ustu pangaramdam ibat king "Space Captain," a kanta da ri [[Joe Cocker]] ampong [[Leon Russell]]. Deng mismung kataya, "lovely planet" la, oneng "lonely planet" ing dimdam nang  Tony Wheeler, at aburi ne.<ref name=Wheeler2007>{{Citation
